tafsir[3]{c,v,t}:
  8,18,"That for you; and that God weakens the unbelievers' guile."
  8,22,"Surely the worst of beasts in God's sight are those that are deaf and dumb and do not understand."
  8,25,"And fear a trial which shall surely not smite in particular the evildoers among you; and know that God is terrible in retribution."